positionInfoEng.locationGuidance: Airside - after Security Checks, turn left and continue to Level 2. Turn right and follow the signs for 'Lounge'. Non-Schengen passengers departing from Gate G are advised to allow sufficient time to pass through passport control. Connections are available for passengers departing from Gates C and D, but please allow sufficient time to get to the departure gate.

Passengers departing from Gates C and D (Schengen flights, non-Schengen flights, connecting flights) have access to the lounge.
